BIB                 10         17
TITLE      Single nucleon transfer reactions near Coulomb
            barrier on 197Au
AUTHOR     (T.Datta, S.P.Dange, H.Naik)
INSTITUTE  (3INDTRM)
REFERENCE  (J,JRN,266,79,2005)
FACILITY   (VDGT,3INDTAT) 14 MeV BARC-TIFR Pelletron facility
SAMPLE     Gold metal foil of thickness 1.5 mg/cm2 or 3.5 mg/cm2
            were used as targets in stacked-foil assemblies
            together with 2.5 um or 7.5 um thick aluminum
            degrader/spacer foils.
DETECTOR   (HPGE) Coupled to a PC based 4096-channel analyzer
            The resolution of the detector system was 2.0 keV at
            1332keV.
METHOD     (GSPEC,STTA)
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) No information about source of uncertainties
HISTORY    (20071030C) AJAY SINGH KALER (ajay18march@gmail.com)
           (20260414A) VT. Entry revised.
